			<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12  order-1 order-md-1 order-sm-first leftcoulmn">
				  <h1 class="title">About Outforce</h1>
				  <p>Outforce brings together employees who are allies of equality in sexual orientation and gender identity, and LGBTQ employees. Along with all our <a href="https://www.salesforce.com/company/equality/equality-groups/" target="_blank">Equality Groups</a>, Outforce also seeks to educate our Salesforce ecosystem on the importance of diversity and inclusion in creating business success. <br>
<br>


The Outforce theme for 2020 is <i>Love Unites Us</i>. The COVID-19 pandemic has left many of us feeling isolated, stressed, and vulnerable and we look towards love to bring us together.

</p>

<p style="text-align:center;">
